{
  "id": "5ba0b7ad6b1bec00131e2448",
  "title": "内部探検と外部探検",
  "created": 1537259441,
  "updated": 1537260450,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ba0b7ad6b1bec00131e2448",
      "text": "内部探検と外部探検",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259441,
      "updated": 1537259441
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b7b0aff09e000016ea3a",
      "text": "[知の探検学]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259441,
      "updated": 1537259462
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b7c6aff09e000016ea3c",
      "text": "\t[探検]に当たって",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259463,
      "updated": 1537259586
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b7deaff09e000016ea3d",
      "text": "\t\tまず[問題提起]が大事",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259487,
      "updated": 1537260450
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b7e3aff09e000016ea3e",
      "text": "\t 次に[探検の五原則]が大事",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259491,
      "updated": 1537259588
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b7efaff09e000016ea3f",
      "text": "   五原則の一つ「[飛び石づたいに]」取材せよ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259503,
      "updated": 1537259590
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b814aff09e000016ea42",
      "text": "   \t近くから遠くへ飛び石づたいに行なうのが自然な順序",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259540,
      "updated": 1537259590
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b820aff09e000016ea43",
      "text": "  \t最も近いのは自分である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259553,
      "updated": 1537259590
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b848aff09e000016ea47",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259592,
      "updated": 1537259592
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b866aff09e000016ea49",
      "text": ">まずわれわれの頭の中を探検せねばならない。そしてこういう探検を、ここでは「[内部探検]」と呼んで、われわれ当事者以外から取材する「[外部探検]」と区別した (p.71)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259623,
      "updated": 1537260354
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b883aff09e000016ea4a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259651,
      "updated": 1537259651
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b8c2aff09e000016ea4f",
      "text": "内部探検も、さらに二段階に区分できる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259714,
      "updated": 1537259725
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b8ccaff09e000016ea53",
      "text": "\t[内省]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259725,
      "updated": 1537259739
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b8dcaff09e000016ea54",
      "text": " \tわれわれ自身の心の奥底の状態、不安、願望",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259740,
      "updated": 1537259802
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b8ecaff09e000016ea55",
      "text": "  これを取り出して[KJ法]で組み立てるのが「[羅針盤作り]」「[問題提起]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259757,
      "updated": 1537260369
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b91baff09e000016ea56",
      "text": "\t[思いだし]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259803,
      "updated": 1537259813
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b8ccaff09e000016ea52",
      "text": "\t\t内省より浅い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259725,
      "updated": 1537259821
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b949aff09e000016ea59",
      "text": "  知識のストック",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259850,
      "updated": 1537259870
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b95eaff09e000016ea5a",
      "text": "  過去の経験など",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259871,
      "updated": 1537259873
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b96aaff09e000016ea5b",
      "text": "  過去に本で読んだり、人に聞いた話など",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259882,
      "updated": 1537259893
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b935aff09e000016ea58",
      "text": "  現在の自分の心の奥底と違って、客観的に眺められる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259829,
      "updated": 1537259844
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b97caff09e000016ea5d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259900,
      "updated": 1537259900
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b97caff09e000016ea5c",
      "text": "内省や思いだしのための方法としてこの後[ブレインストーミング]が紹介される",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259900,
      "updated": 1537259922
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b9ddaff09e000016ea5f",
      "text": "オズボーンのブレインストーミングの原則に、川喜田二郎なりの解釈が加えられ、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259997,
      "updated": 1537260008
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0baa9aff09e000016ea60",
      "text": "[ブレインストーミングの四原則は探検の五原則に包含される]、と言う主張をする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537260202,
      "updated": 1537260385
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba0b97eaff09e000016ea5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537259903,
      "updated": 1537259903
    }
  ]
}